Turaglas, the Ebon Maw, is the Abyssal+lord of hunger and consumption. Once the ruler of the 32nd layer of the Abyss, Sholo-Tovoth, Turaglas was imprisoned by his rivals Orcus and Demogorgon.
One of the oldest of Tanar'ri, Turaglas was spawned by the Abyss a million years ago.
Sources: 
Fiendish Codex I: Hordes of the Abyss, page 156
Dragon #312